title: Final Quarter
name: Lunar Phase - Final Quarter
printed_effect:
Search your deck for up to 2 Lunar Phase
and send them to your Underworld.
When this Lunar Phase is discarded by
another Lunar Phase you can return {lunar} from
your Underworld to your Spirit Deck.
